item.title: CVE-2017-11461|2024-09-17T00:26:39.580Z -- netapp -- oncommand%20unified%20manager
item.description: NetApp OnCommand Unified Manager for 7-mode (core package) versions prior to 5.2.1 are susceptible to a clickjacking or "UI redress attack" which could be used to cause a user to perform an unintended action in the user interface.
